text: Jacqueline Martel (11 February 1927 - January 2015) was a French alpine skier. She competed in two events at the 1952 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1927 births Category:2015 deaths Category:French female alpine skiers Category:Olympic alpine skiers of France Category:Alpine skiers at the 1952 Winter Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Haute-Savoie
